The effective POM resolver (com.arvindand.mcp.maven.pom) is an independent
implementation. Its algorithm shape — parent chain walking, property
interpolation, dependencyManagement merge, and <scope>import</scope> BOM
resolution — follows the MIT-licensed maxxq-org/maxxq-maven library by
Guy Chauliac (https://github.com/maxxq-org/maxxq-maven), scoped to
declared-dep resolution (no transitive dependency walking).
